Apa saja orang buat untuk aku, aku tetap syukur.

518
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:27,500
Emak aku memang ajar aku macam tu dari kecil.

519
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:30,880
Kalau orang bagi aku barang,

520
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:33,080
atau nampak orang tua tak beri salam,

521
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:35,480
Emak aku garang tau.

522
00:31:37,260 --> 00:31:39,040
Aku pernah tengok.

523
00:31:39,700 --> 00:31:40,860
Kau pernah tengok ke?

524
00:31:41,270 --> 00:31:42,150
Maksud kau...

525
00:31:42,510 --> 00:31:44,340
Kau nampak sendiri emak aku garang ke?

526
00:31:52,020 --> 00:31:54,280
- Mama - Sini, mari

527
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:57,800
- Sini cepat, kau dah mula tipu mama - Aduh, mama

528
00:31:58,040 --> 00:32:00,180
Dalam fikiran asyik main game je ya?

529
00:32:00,360 --> 00:32:03,360
Dah lewat tak balik, keluarga risau tau!

530
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:07,480
- Jangan buat lagi - Mama...

531
00:32:08,180 --> 00:32:09,780
Mama buat saya malu depan kawan-kawan.

532
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,480
Saya tak ada pun.

533
00:32:11,700 --> 00:32:13,040
Tolong la...

534
00:32:14,140 --> 00:32:15,720
Maaf.

535
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:18,240
Saya salah.

536
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:20,500
Tak payah minta maaf sekarang.

537
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:24,900
Mama cubit telinga saya...

538
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:27,900
Pergelangan tangan mama sakit ke? Saya risau.

539
00:32:29,820 --> 00:32:32,160
Jom kita makan sedap-sedap nak?

540
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:34,240
Lepas makan nanti mesti rasa gembira.

541
00:32:35,190 --> 00:32:35,870
Tolonglah, mama...

542
00:32:37,580 --> 00:32:39,270
Makan sikit je makanan sedap.

543
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:41,340
Dah makan sedap, senang hati. Jom.

544
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:44,500
Tengok, dah senyum.

545
00:32:46,010 --> 00:32:47,940
- Jom makan - Baiklah

546
00:32:49,340 --> 00:32:51,380
Mesti sedap, kan? Jom lah.

547
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:53,840
Kau cakap kau pernah tengok...

548
00:32:54,210 --> 00:32:55,530
Mana mungkin.

549
00:33:02,950 --> 00:33:04,550
Aku pun nak tanya kau satu benda.

550
00:33:07,540 --> 00:33:09,430
Dulu kau cakap kau suka aku.

551
00:33:11,730 --> 00:33:12,920
Kenapa ya?

552
00:33:14,020 --> 00:33:15,430
Ceritalah sikit lagi.

553
00:33:17,970 --> 00:33:19,850
Tolonglah...

554
00:33:19,950 --> 00:33:21,920
Beritahu aku, boleh?

555
00:33:23,040 --> 00:33:24,290
Kau nak tahu sangat ke?

556
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,740
Ya, aku nak tahu.

557
00:33:27,290 --> 00:33:28,820
Aku tak nak beritahu.

558
00:33:29,010 --> 00:33:29,960
Hoi.

559
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:35,350
Kau tengok muka kau tu.

560
00:33:40,570 --> 00:33:41,380
Hoi.

561
00:33:42,800 --> 00:33:45,530
Sukan sekolah dah nak mula.

562
00:33:45,640 --> 00:33:46,850
Aku teruja sangat!

563
00:33:47,900 --> 00:33:48,930
Kenapa?

564
00:33:49,110 --> 00:33:49,830
Yang ni...

565
00:33:50,900 --> 00:33:52,920
Sebab tak payah masuk kelas.

566
00:33:54,890 --> 00:33:56,400
Tak payah belajar, boleh rehat!

567
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:12,570
Bila nak mula ya?

568
00:34:12,810 --> 00:34:13,960
Tak lama lagi.

569
00:34:15,990 --> 00:34:18,590
Foam, kau kipas sangat, sejuklah!

570
00:34:18,790 --> 00:34:21,180
Hari ni panas gila weh.

571
00:34:21,370 --> 00:34:22,670
Aku sampai berpeluh habis.

572
00:34:22,730 --> 00:34:23,880
Apa yang buat kau risau sangat?

573
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,630
Ke sebab kau tak pernah couple dengan perempuan?

574
00:34:25,630 --> 00:34:29,350
Jangan perasanlah. Aku pergi dulu, bye!

575
00:34:29,450 --> 00:34:30,300
Hoi!

576
00:34:31,340 --> 00:34:33,300
Dia nak ke mana tu?

577
00:34:34,090 --> 00:34:35,980
Pergi tengok awek la tu. Biarlah dia.

578
00:34:36,240 --> 00:34:37,370
Jom naik ke pentas, nak?

579
00:34:37,810 --> 00:34:39,430
Okey.

580
00:34:41,770 --> 00:34:46,820
Seterusnya naik pentas, pelajar fakulti perubatan.

581
00:35:19,190 --> 00:35:21,790
Sayang sekali, tak bawa kamera.

582
00:35:21,830 --> 00:35:23,930
Aku nak ambil gambar.

583
00:35:24,610 --> 00:35:25,270
Ah.

584
00:35:26,200 --> 00:35:29,050
Nak ambil gambar? Akhirnya bukan
langit je kali ni?

585
00:35:30,390 --> 00:35:34,870
Langit yang disinari lampu pentas.

586
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,830
Mungkin akan nampak cantik.

587
00:35:41,970 --> 00:35:43,570
Kau rasa akan hujan ke?

588
00:35:44,740 --> 00:35:47,310
Mungkin. Selalu hujan waktu ni
setiap tahun.

589
00:35:49,410 --> 00:35:50,230
Tapi...

590
00:35:50,540 --> 00:35:52,720
Kalau hujan, mesti seronok.

591
00:35:54,190 --> 00:35:55,010
Betul juga.

592
00:36:04,910 --> 00:36:06,350
Gembira tak?

593
00:36:08,580 --> 00:36:09,880
Ya, aku sangat gembira.

594
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:12,390
Masa kau atas pentas tadi...

595
00:36:12,570 --> 00:36:14,250
Ter langsung tak boleh alih mata.

596
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:15,390
Phoon.

597
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:18,020
Ya, aku nampak.

598
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:21,850
Aku tak tengok.

599
00:36:24,390 --> 00:36:27,620
Aku suka kau tak tengok orang lain.

600
00:36:35,030 --> 00:36:36,840
Aku nak cari Foam.

601
00:36:37,120 --> 00:36:38,700
- Kau duduk sini ye. - Kenapa nak balik sekarang?

602
00:36:38,750 --> 00:36:39,780
Kau duduk sini saja.

603
00:36:39,970 --> 00:36:41,700
- Aku serah Ter pada kau. - Tiada masalah.

604
00:36:41,980 --> 00:36:42,700
Hei.

605
00:36:47,320 --> 00:36:50,100
Dah letih berdiri? Mari cari tempat duduk.

606
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:50,840
Okey.

607
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:55,750
Kau dah perkenalkan dia secara rasmi?

608
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:57,430
Jangan layan kawan aku sambil lewa tau.

609
00:36:57,510 --> 00:36:59,790
Korang, tengok teman lelaki Hill!

610
00:37:11,270 --> 00:37:12,760
Tengok apa tu?

611
00:37:13,140 --> 00:37:14,400
Tak ada apa.

612
00:37:15,590 --> 00:37:17,070
Aku cuma fikir...

613
00:37:17,970 --> 00:37:19,840
Jika kau sentiasa tersenyum macam ni,

614
00:37:19,890 --> 00:37:23,210
apa saja aku sanggup buat.

615
00:37:24,670 --> 00:37:26,200
Cukup, P'Hill.

616
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:28,700
Tak tunjuk lagi.

617
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:32,780
Jangan main-mainlah.

618
00:37:38,850 --> 00:37:40,790
Setiap tahun waktu ni memang hujan ke?

619
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:45,190
Ya, dah beberapa tahun macam ni.

620
00:37:45,710 --> 00:37:47,780
Dah jadi sebahagian acara sukan.

621
00:37:54,240 --> 00:37:55,130
Jom kita pergi.

622
00:37:55,250 --> 00:37:56,980
Mari.

623
00:38:27,130 --> 00:38:28,560
Buat apa tu, P'Hill?

624
00:38:29,390 --> 00:38:30,620
Biar aku peluk kau.

625
00:38:32,210 --> 00:38:32,920
P'Hill.

626
00:38:33,560 --> 00:38:34,900
Geli la.

627
00:38:35,240 --> 00:38:36,360
Masih tak biasa ke?

628
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:40,090
- Tak lagi. - Tak biasa lagi?

629
00:38:40,490 --> 00:38:41,510
P'Hill.

630
00:38:42,080 --> 00:38:42,900
Sedap tak?

631
00:38:43,510 --> 00:38:44,530
Sedap.

632
00:38:49,650 --> 00:38:51,630
- Semua untuk aku ke? - Semua untuk kau.

633
00:38:52,890 --> 00:38:53,870
Sedap tak?

634
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:56,240
- Terlalu manis. - Kenapa?

635
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:58,230
Kau tak suka ke?

636
00:38:58,630 --> 00:39:00,190
- Kalau tak suka, aku makan. - Aku suka.

637
00:39:02,450 --> 00:39:04,170
Gurau je.

638
00:39:04,530 --> 00:39:07,180
Biar aku tengok muka comel kau.

639
00:39:08,620 --> 00:39:09,580
Senyum sikit.

640
00:39:10,220 --> 00:39:11,230
Muncung sikit.

641
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:12,770
Muka itik.

642
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:14,550
Muka itik.

643
00:39:16,380 --> 00:39:17,460
Jom, jom.

644
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:23,360
Jahatlah kau ni.

645
00:39:31,020 --> 00:39:32,240
Hujan dah berhenti.

646
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:40,730
Awan dah reda, bintang pun dah keluar.

647
00:39:40,730 --> 00:39:42,030
Cantiknya.

648
00:39:45,210 --> 00:39:46,160
Ya.

649
00:39:50,220 --> 00:39:51,050
Jadi...

650
00:39:51,290 --> 00:39:53,850
Kau nak tengok pemandangan ni hari-hari?

651
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:57,930
Maksud kau nak aku duduk sekali?

652
00:39:58,710 --> 00:39:59,660
Ya.

653
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:03,570
Gila ke apa? Aku tak nak.

654
00:40:05,430 --> 00:40:06,570
Kenapa tak nak?

655
00:40:08,700 --> 00:40:09,600
Aku rayu lah.

656
00:40:10,520 --> 00:40:12,320
Aku tak mampu bayar sewa sini.

657
00:40:13,250 --> 00:40:13,990
Hei.

658
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:16,230
Aku takkan bagi kau bayar pun.

659
00:40:17,710 --> 00:40:19,100
Kau nak aku duduk sini percuma?

660
00:40:19,310 --> 00:40:20,080
Mestilah.

661
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:21,360
Tapi takpe.

662
00:40:21,590 --> 00:40:22,880
Aku rasa segan lah.

663
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:26,400
Tak apa.

664
00:40:26,570 --> 00:40:28,800
Semua orang nak jaga orang tersayang, kan?

665
00:40:28,890 --> 00:40:29,840
Betul kan?

666
00:40:33,100 --> 00:40:35,160
Aku tak boleh datang. Aku risaukan North.

667
00:40:35,380 --> 00:40:38,060
Dia tak pandai hidup sendiri.

668
00:40:38,300 --> 00:40:39,410
North.

669
00:40:41,310 --> 00:40:42,350
Aku akan uruskan.

670
00:40:43,850 --> 00:40:46,240
Uruskan? Macam mana? Nak buat apa dekat dia?

671
00:40:46,460 --> 00:40:47,970
- Aku tak setuju. - Hei.

672
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,870
Kalau kau apa-apakan dia, aku marah.

673
00:40:50,680 --> 00:40:52,170
Aku takkan buat apa-apa pada North.

674
00:40:52,720 --> 00:40:54,840
Kau fikir aku sejahat tu ke?

675
00:40:54,950 --> 00:40:55,720
Entahlah.

676
00:40:56,090 --> 00:40:57,470
Mana tahu.

677
00:40:58,750 --> 00:41:00,200
Aku rasa...

678
00:41:00,410 --> 00:41:02,760
North pun mungkin pindah tempat lain.

679
00:41:04,140 --> 00:41:05,410
Macam mana kau tahu?

680
00:41:06,380 --> 00:41:08,320
Aku agak je.

681
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:11,910
North, dia nak pindah ke mana?

682
00:41:13,670 --> 00:41:15,060
Dia tak pernah cakap.

683
00:41:17,730 --> 00:41:18,620
Dia tak nak bagitahu aku.

684
00:41:24,950 --> 00:41:26,340
P'Hill, buat apa tu?

685
00:41:26,390 --> 00:41:27,960
P'Hill.

686
00:41:28,460 --> 00:41:30,580
Janganlah, P'Hill! Jangan ambil gambar.

687
00:41:30,710 --> 00:41:31,870
- Satu dua lagi. - Tak nak.

688
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,360
Tunjuklah.

689
00:41:33,930 --> 00:41:35,190
Comelnya.

690
00:41:36,180 --> 00:41:37,470
Padam lah! Padam!

691
00:41:37,560 --> 00:41:39,770
Mari sini, aku tunjuk gambar.

692
00:41:40,670 --> 00:41:42,250
Senyum.

693
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:45,150
Senyum.

694
00:41:46,330 --> 00:41:47,640
Biar aku tengok.

695
00:41:48,910 --> 00:41:49,750
Tengok sini.

696
00:41:50,120 --> 00:41:51,600
- Cantik kan? - Comel sangat.

697
00:41:51,640 --> 00:41:52,760
Pandai kau ambil gambar.

698
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:55,280
Boleh aku kongsi?

699
00:41:59,500 --> 00:42:01,857
(Senyuman aku bukan untuk kamera,
tapi untuk jurugambar.)

700
00:42:05,100 --> 00:42:06,800
Buat apa tu?

701
00:42:10,020 --> 00:42:11,440
Kau malu ke?

702
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:13,780
Tak pun.

703
00:42:14,110 --> 00:42:15,260
Tak malu ke?

704
00:42:15,730 --> 00:42:17,020
- Tak. - Betul tak malu?

705
00:42:17,090 --> 00:42:17,720
Takde.

706
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:18,860
Betul ke?

707
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:21,700
- Tak malu. - Tunjuk muka malu sikit.

708
00:42:22,190 --> 00:42:22,810
Apa ni...

709
00:42:22,820 --> 00:42:23,410
Kat mana?

710
00:42:24,810 --> 00:42:26,110
Tapi comel juga.

711
00:42:27,640 --> 00:42:28,680
P'Hill.

712
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:30,900
- Kau mesti dah merah muka. - Tak la.

713
00:42:30,960 --> 00:42:31,820
P'Hill.

714
00:42:32,090 --> 00:42:33,350
- Tak merah ke? - Tak.

715
00:42:33,450 --> 00:42:36,150
Jangan la, tak nak macam ni.

716
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:38,290
- Betul tak merah ke? - P'Hill.

717
00:42:38,540 --> 00:42:39,440
Cukuplah kacau.

718
00:42:39,730 --> 00:42:41,810
Betul ke?

719
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:47,550
P'Hill, sudah.

720
00:43:31,860 --> 00:43:34,510
Pusingan ni, markah tertinggi
jatuh pada...

721
00:43:34,570 --> 00:43:37,170
Ratchakit. Dia dapat 60 markah penuh.

722
00:43:37,190 --> 00:43:39,720
Semua, tepuk tangan sikit.

723
00:43:43,810 --> 00:43:45,930
Hill, kau memang hebat.

724
00:43:45,990 --> 00:43:47,240
Cuma separuh kelas lulus.

725
00:43:47,240 --> 00:43:49,080
Kau dapat markah penuh pula.

726
00:43:52,460 --> 00:43:56,330
Ratchakit, jumpa saya lepas kelas.

727
00:43:57,330 --> 00:43:58,000
Baik.

728
00:44:04,670 --> 00:44:05,950
Kau buat dengan baik.

729
00:44:06,070 --> 00:44:09,120
Kau satu-satunya yg dapat penuh.

730
00:44:10,310 --> 00:44:12,350
Ujian kali ni sangat susah.

731
00:44:12,530 --> 00:44:13,560
Bagus kerja kau.

732
00:44:13,960 --> 00:44:15,570
Teruskan usaha.

733
00:44:19,470 --> 00:44:22,020
Aku akan hantar markah kau pada atuk kau.

734
00:44:28,480 --> 00:44:30,560
Kau mesti tertekan, kan?

735
00:44:42,480 --> 00:44:45,490
Kau pernah buat benda yang aku bangga?

736
00:44:47,860 --> 00:44:49,650
Itu benda lain, ayah.

737
00:44:49,850 --> 00:44:51,270
Mana boleh tak berkait?

738
00:44:51,470 --> 00:44:53,400
Aku rancang masa depan cucu aku.

739
00:44:53,420 --> 00:44:55,740
Agar dia tidak tercicir.

740
00:44:57,980 --> 00:44:59,580
Tapi itu masa depan dia.

741
00:45:00,110 --> 00:45:01,460
Biar dia pilih sendiri.

742
00:45:01,930 --> 00:45:04,520
Tapi kau paksa dia tuisyen lebih-lebih.

743
00:45:04,650 --> 00:45:06,940
Tak keterlaluan ke?

744
00:45:10,640 --> 00:45:12,480
Kalau aku ikut cakap kau...

745
00:45:13,030 --> 00:45:14,840
Boleh tak kamu berdua jangan gaduh?

746
00:45:18,810 --> 00:45:19,650
Tak, tak.

747
00:45:20,070 --> 00:45:21,420
Bukan macam tu, anak.

748
00:45:21,650 --> 00:45:22,760
Aku cuma...

749
00:45:23,200 --> 00:45:25,490
Tak nak kau lalui hidup aku dulu.

750
00:45:29,300 --> 00:45:30,520
Aku nak kau macam budak lain,

751
00:45:30,520 --> 00:45:31,560
hidup normal, gembira main.

752
00:45:37,830 --> 00:45:38,780
Aku okey saja.

753
00:46:42,790 --> 00:46:44,290
Hei.

754
00:46:44,950 --> 00:46:46,220
Kejap.

755
00:46:46,560 --> 00:46:49,520
Kenapa kau berdiri sorang-sorang kat gelap?

756
00:46:54,580 --> 00:46:56,560
Tunggu mak ayah ke?

757
00:46:58,520 --> 00:47:00,710
Boleh tunggu dalam saja.

758
00:47:00,830 --> 00:47:03,000
Sini gelap, bahaya tau.

759
00:47:06,840 --> 00:47:08,960
Mari masuk, jangan takut. Mari.

760
00:47:09,500 --> 00:47:11,140
Masuk tunggu kat dalam, mari.

761
00:47:18,730 --> 00:47:20,540
Duduk dalam sini ye.

762
00:47:20,580 --> 00:47:24,380
Malam-malam nyamuk banyak kat luar.

763
00:47:25,440 --> 00:47:27,680
Duduk dalam rumah saja, jangan segan.

764
00:47:28,990 --> 00:47:30,210
Kau lapar tak?

765
00:47:30,550 --> 00:47:32,770
Kedai kopi aku ada pencuci mulut.

766
00:47:32,890 --> 00:47:34,470
Nak makan sesuatu?

767
00:47:35,280 --> 00:47:37,090
Mari, tengok ni.

768
00:47:37,250 --> 00:47:39,040
Tak makan pun tak apa.

769
00:47:47,490 --> 00:47:48,850
Kek kelapa.

770
00:47:49,240 --> 00:47:52,550
Entah ada lagi tak... Sekejap ya.

771
00:47:52,770 --> 00:47:53,830
